OL,3,CProsecutors to decide whether to seek
OL,4,Cthird trial in airport assault case
OL,6,FProsecutors are expected to decide
OL,7,Fwhether to pursue a third trial of two
OL,8,Fbrothers accused of assaulting a
OL,9,Fpolice officer at Manchester Airport.
OL,11,FMohammed Fahir Amaaz, 21, and Muhammad
OL,12,FAmaad, 26, are accused of using a
OL,13,F"high level of violence" to cause
OL,14,Factual bodily harm to Pc Zachary
OL,15,FMarsden during a confrontation in July
OL,16,F2024 that went viral on social media.
OL,18,FBoth men denied the charge, telling
OL,19,FLiverpool Crown Court they acted in
OL,20,Fself-defence or in defence of each
OL,21,Fother.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@XO]
