OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1780074357
OL,3,CProsecutors to decide whether to seek
OL,4,Cthird trial in airport assault case
OL,6,FJudge Neil Flewitt KC discharged the
OL,7,Fjury after nearly 20 hours of
OL,8,Fdeliberations, but on Friday the Crown
OL,9,FProsecution Service is expected to
OL,10,Fdecide whether they want to seek a
OL,11,Fthird trial.
OL,13,FLast July, Amaaz was found guilty of
OL,14,Fassaulting Pc Lydia Ward and Pc Ellie
OL,15,FCook during the same incident on July
OL,16,F23.
OL,18,FA retrial was ordered last year after
OL,19,Fno verdict was reached against him or
OL,20,Fhis brother on the Pc Marsden
OL,21,Fallegation.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
