CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1780074357
OL,3,CProsecutors to decide whether to seek
OL,4,Cthird trial in airport assault case
OL,6,FThe three Greater Manchester Police
OL,7,Fofficers entered the Terminal 2 car
OL,8,Fpark paystation after reports that a
OL,9,Fmale fitting Amaaz's description had
OL,10,Fheadbutted a member of the public at a
OL,11,FStarbucks cafe in the airport minutes
OL,12,Fearlier.
OL,14,FThe prosecution said Amaaz resisted
OL,15,Ftheir attempts to take him outside and
OL,16,FAmaad then intervened.
OL,18,FBut the brothers, from Rochdale,
OL,19,FGreater Manchester, said their actions
OL,20,Fwere defensive rather than offensive
OL,21,Fas they said they came "under attack".
OL,26,@}D@XOU}D@eO]
