PN,39704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1780074357
OL,3,CProsecutors to decide whether to seek
OL,4,Cthird trial in airport assault case
OL,6,FPc Ward suffered a broken nose as she
OL,7,Fwas floored by a punch to the face
OL,8,Ffrom Amaaz, who also knocked Pc Cook
OL,9,Fto the ground with a series of elbows
OL,10,Fand punches.
OL,12,FAmaaz claimed he did not realise Pc
OL,13,FWard and Pc Cook were women as "it was
OL,14,Fhappening so fast, I couldn't process
OL,15,Fthe little details".
OL,17,FHe was also convicted at the previous
OL,18,Ftrial of assaulting the member of the
OL,19,Fpublic, Abdulkareem Ismaeil, in
OL,20,FStarbucks.
OL,26,@uD@`OUwD@SO]
