OL,3,CProsecutors to decide whether to seek
OL,4,Cthird trial in airport assault case
OL,6,FGreater Manchester Police said they
OL,7,Fwere "disappointed" that a verdict
OL,8,Fcould not be reached by a jury in the
OL,9,Fretrial.
OL,26,@oD@FOUoD@SO]
